## 🔐 SECURITY

> **AI: Read this before touching auth, input handling, data access, or any user-facing boundary.**
> **Never implement a security-relevant feature without checking this section first.**

### Authentication model
- **Auth method:** Cookie-based session (`ZENITH_SESSION`). Single user (admin/blasco).
- **Token storage:** httpOnly cookie (set via `Set-Cookie` header on POST /login).
- **Token lifetime:** Session length (no expiry). Token is a random hex string stored in `tokenSesionActiva`.
- **Auth check location:** `estaLogueado()` in web_server.cpp:29.

### Authorization model
- **Model:** Flat — one user (admin). Full access to everything.
- **Roles defined:** None (single user).
- **Permission check location:** `estaLogueado()` on every protected route.

### Sensitive data inventory
| Data | Location in code | Storage | Encryption |
|------|-----------------|---------|-----------|
| WiFi password | config.cpp:6 | Firmware flash (compiled binary) | None |
| Web login password | web_server.cpp (hardcoded) | Firmware flash (compiled binary) | None |
| Session token | tokenSesionActiva (RAM) | Runtime variable | None |
| NFC block data | bloqueEscaneado / bloque0Habitacion | RAM | None |

### Input validation rules
- Web login: `server.arg("user")` and `server.arg("pass")` compared as strings.
- File API: filename parameter from query string, written directly to LittleFS path.
- WebSocket commands: forwarded directly to Core 1 for FSM processing.
- **No input sanitization or length validation present.**

### Attack surface
| Surface | Risk | Mitigation in place |
|---------|------|-------------------|
| Web file API (read/write/delete) | Arbitrary file access | Session cookie check only |
| WebSocket | Command injection into Telnet CLI | None — commands executed as-is |
| OTA | Unauthorized firmware flash | ArduinoOTA default (no password set) |
| Telnet (port 23) | Unauthenticated CLI access | Session guard (`!telnetClient.connected()` reject) |
| No TLS | Credentials sent in plaintext | No mitigation |

